title: Live ACL: Roar v Ulsan, WSW v Oscar’s Shanghai
text:
Oscar can predict the future 0:34 Live Asian Champions League: Ulsan FC v Brisbane Roar, Shanghai SIPG v Western Sydney Wanderers February 28, 2017 6:28pm by Staff writers Source: FOX SPORTS BRISBANE Roar face Ulsan FC from 9:30pm AEDT while Western Sydney Wanderers take on Shanghai SIPG from 10:30pm on Asian Champions League matchday two. 
Former Roar star Dimitri Petratos could line up for Ulsan at Ulsan Munsu football stadium, while ex-Chelsea player Oscar will be SIPG’s biggest threat against the Wanderers at Shanghai Stadium. 
Follow Brisbane’s match live on Fox Sports 505 from 9:30pm and the Wanderers’ clash on Fox Sports 504 from 10:30pm.
